{"id":291246,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-各地上访维权人士在京祭奠林昭（图）/","date":"2013-04-30T04:30:54Z","modified":"2013-04-30T04:30:54Z","title":"维权网 | 各地上访维权人士在京祭奠林昭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>是林昭牺牲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>周年纪念日，在京维权访民打出《怀念林昭民主自由人权宪政》的横幅纪念这位民主的先驱者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>林昭于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1954</span><span>年以江苏省第一名的成绩考入北大，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1957</span><span>年反右运动中被划为右派，因“反革命罪”于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1960</span><span>年起关押在上海提篮桥监狱，被长期监禁。林昭在狱中坚持自己的信仰，拒绝认罪，她在狱中写二十万字血书表达追求自由、平等之信念。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1968</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>被秘密枪决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1980</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>，上海高级法院“沪高刑复字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">435</span><span>号”刑事判决书，宣布林昭以精神病为由平反为无罪，结论为“这是一次冤杀无辜”，并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1980</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月在北京举行追悼会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1981</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，上海高院改正错误，又以“沪高刑申字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2346</span><span>号”刑事判决书撤销了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1980</span><span>年“沪高刑复字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">435</span><span>号”判决书，认定前判决书宣告林昭无罪的理由为精神病不妥。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权访民们说：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>年前的今天，年仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">36</span><span>岁的林昭被秘密枪决。她为的是中国的民主大业。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1981</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，上海市高级法院以“沪高刑申字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2346</span><span>号”对林昭彻底平反。我们希望当局向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>年前的今天一样拿出勇气，纠正现在的冤假错案。否则我们一定会继承林昭的遗志不怕流血牺牲，继续反腐维权，为实现民主宪政大业奋斗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加怀念林昭活动的有：上海项文寅、吴玉芬、郑培培、陈载忠；山西彭静梅；江苏汤树秀；辽宁赵广军、刘丽、杨淑梅；吉林赵云侠、邓志波、陈凤杰、王桂香；黑龙江杜青艳、陈秀娟、陈惠娟；天津郑建慧等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}